snippet.description:

Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-afghanistan-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700001384

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

It was a thriller of a match when Sri Lanka and Afghanistan faced each other in the first ODI. Sri Lanka posted a massive total of 381 runs on the board and Pathum Nissanka scored a brilliant double-century in the process. During the chase, Afghanistan lost five wickets in quick succession but a superb partnership between Azmatullah Omarzai and Mohammad Nabi took them near the target. In the end, it was Sri Lanka who sealed a victory after winning by 42 runs.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | MAGIC | Diljit Dosanjh x The Quickstyle
snippet.description:
Love stories from the heartland have inspired generations across the globe. Bringing real magic from the pind of Punjab to the world stage. The OG 'Lover' himself, Diljit Dosanjh is back at Coke Studio Bharat to show us how to fall in love all over again. Relive the moment of your first infatuation, of falling in love through the depth of your eyes. Uplifting this song with their electrifying presence â€˜The Quick Styleâ€™, make you groove and an add a whole lot of heart to the first song of Coke Studio Bharat 2024

snippet.title: 'Boss Vs BossğŸ˜' Triple H REJECTS The Rock, Roman Reigns Vs Cody Rhodes - WWE Smackdown Highlights
snippet.description:
Topics Covered In Video-
1) WWE Smackdown 9 February 2024 highlights & full show results in Hindi
2) Triple H takes shots at The Rock
3) Roman Reigns will defend his title against Cody Rhodes
4) The Rock & Roman Reigns to return to Smackdown
5) WWE Elimination Chamber 2024 qualifying matches

#wwe #smackdown #therock #romanreigns #tripleh 

'Boss Vs BossğŸ˜' Triple H REJECTS The Rock, Roman Reigns Vs Cody Rhodes - WWE Smackdown Highlights

Experience the explosive WWE Smackdown highlights from February 9, 2024, featuring heart-stopping action and unforgettable moments. Immerse yourself in the full show, witnessing electrifying clashes and high-flying maneuvers that define Smackdown. Watch as The Rock makes his long-awaited return, igniting the arena with his unmatched charisma. Witness the epic showdown between The Rock and Triple H, as old rivalries reignite. Feel the seismic impact as Roman Reigns and The Rock unite, forming an unstoppable force. Don't miss a second of the adrenaline-pumping excitement as WWE Smackdown delivers another unforgettable episode packed with thrills and drama.

The segment featuring Triple H, Nick Aldis, Adam Pearce, and Drew McIntyre kicked off with a bang, setting the stage for an electrifying night on SmackDown. Triple H, the authority figure, took center stage, asserting his dominance and clarifying the path to WrestleMania. With unwavering confidence, he declared the main event matchup and made it clear that he's the ultimate decision-maker.
Nick Aldis stepped in to announce the next big challenge, shifting focus to the World Heavyweight Championship scene. With a united front, WWE Management laid out plans for an Elimination Chamber match to determine the challenger for Seth Rollins. This decision showcased the collaborative effort behind the scenes to ensure a thrilling road to WrestleMania.
Adam Pearce then outlined the lineup for the Elimination Chamber, featuring top-tier superstars vying for a shot at championship glory. The intense competition and high stakes set the stage for an epic showdown.
Drew McIntyre, fueled by determination and a desire to prove himself, made his presence known. With a fiery speech, he laid out his path to WrestleMania, promising to overcome all obstacles and emerge victorious for the WWE Universe.
The action heated up with the first match of the night, a hard-hitting showdown between McIntyre and AJ Styles. The back-and-forth battle showcased the raw athleticism and tenacity of both competitors, with McIntyre ultimately securing the win and advancing in the Elimination Chamber race.
As the night unfolded, backstage interviews provided insight into the mindset of other contenders like Sami Zayn and Randy Orton, each determined to seize their moment on the road to WrestleMania.
The tension continued to build with confrontations between rival factions and personal revelations, setting the stage for future clashes and storyline developments.
Overall, the segment featuring Triple H, Nick Aldis, Adam Pearce, and Drew McIntyre delivered a thrilling mix of intrigue, competition, and anticipation as the journey to WrestleMania reached new heights.

05:17 Qualification Match chamber
05:25 The Rock & Roman Reigns to return

snippet.title: The Bacardi Song: Rinosh George ft. Lachu | New Malayalam Music Video 2024
snippet.description:
Rinosh George is back with another music video just in time for Valentine's season! 

Get ready to swoon all over again as he brings the romantic vibes back. It's gonna be one of those videos that'll make your heart skip a beat!

And guess what? It's not just Rinosh, but also the stunning Lachu making an appearance in this video! Double the charm, double the smiles.

Get ready to be amused when you see these two beauties together!

Video Credits:
Director: Rinosh George
Producers: Arosh John, Rinosh George 
DOP: Luke Jose 
Editor and Colorist: Sagar Saseedaran 
Stylist: Rida Nawab 
Video Sound Design: Nikhil Mukkatira

Audio Credits:
Lyricist, Music Composer, and singer: Rinosh George 
Music Produced,Programmed & Arranged by Hriday Goswami 
Guitar: Tony Das 
Bass Guitar: Prashanth Gnanamuthu
Choir Arranged and Conducted by Hriday Goswami 
Backing Vox: Ruhee Ahmed 
Song mixed and mastered by Hriday Goswami at X-noise studio Guwahati
Recorded in Pranava Studios,Bangalore




#rinoshgeorge #lachu #music

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

How To Make Bio Diesel At Home From Vegetable Oil...

Thanks For Watching, Love You Titanium Army.

Biodiesel is a renewable, biodegradable fuel manufactured domestically from vegetable oils, animal fats, or recycled restaurant grease. Biodiesel meets both the biomass-based diesel and overall advanced biofuel requirement of the Renewable Fuel Standard.

How To Make Biodiesel From Vegetable Oil - 

How to Make Biodiesel

1. You want to prepare the biodiesel in a room that is at least 60 degrees C because the chemical reaction will not proceed to completion if the temperature is too low.

2. label all your containers as "Toxicâ€”Only Use for Making Biodiesel.

3. Wear Protective Gloves And Other Apparatus 

4. Mix the methanol and sodium hydroxide until the sodium hydroxide has completely dissolved then add vegetable oil ( 60 Degree C ) to this mixture.

5. Continue blending this mixture Slowly for 20 to 30 minutes.

6. Pour the mixture into a widemouthed jar. You will see the liquid start to separate out into layers. The bottom layer will be glycerin. The top layer is biodiesel.

7. Allow at least a couple of hours for the mixture to fully separate. You want to keep the top layer as your biodiesel fuel. If you like, you can keep the glycerin for other projects. You can either carefully pour off the biodiesel or use a pump or baster to pull the biodiesel off of the glycerin.

8. You Should Wash Biodiesel at least 5 times with water.

Biodiesel can be used in several ways, but it's important to consider your specific context and vehicle compatibility before trying it.

Compatibility: Most modern diesel engines can handle low blends of biodiesel (B5 or B20) without modification. Check your vehicle owner's manual for specific recommendations. Higher blends (B50, B100) may require modifications and are not always recommended.

snippet.title: LADDU | 1000 MOTICHOOR LADDU | Sweet and Soft Laddu Recipe Cooking in Village | Boondi Laddu Making
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 1000 Motichoor Laddu using crushed pearls. Normally, laddu is made with Boondi, but Motichoor laddu is made using smashed Boondi. That is why Moticoor Laddu is special and so soft.

The taste is Yummy!

snippet.title: Disclaimer: Not your regular interview| Shark Tank India 3| Vineeta Singh| Aman Gupta| Anupam Mittal
snippet.description:
After the stupendous success of the business reality shows two seasons, the makers came up Shark Tank India 3. While its all about the pitches, what makes this show stand out are its Sharks aka the investors. The panel consists 12 investors and Pinkvilla chanced upon its four sharks, Vineeta Singh, Anupam Mittal, Ritesh Agarwal and Aman Gupta for an exclusive chat. They ensured that you laughed your guts out and how thick their friendship is. Watch the video till the end.

Episode 155: The Kidnapper's Game
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Aradhna is trapped inside a secret room by a mysterious kidnapper. Vikram and Pooja find a bloody trunk outside their house. The kidnapper threatens Reyansh to stop his investigation if he wants Aradhna to live. Meanwhile, Bhakti starts to regain her consciousness.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.
